# Simple Calculator App

A clean, browser-based calculator that performs basic arithmetic operations: addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division.

## Features
- Basic operations: `+`, `-`, `*`, `/`
- Clear button (`C`) to reset the display
- Responsive and mobile-friendly design

## Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

## Live Demo
[View Calculator App](https://yadrielpereyra.github.io/calculator-app/)

## How to Use
1. Click on the numbers and operators to build your calculation.
2. Press `=` to see the result.
3. Press `C` to clear and start over.

